 ecommended so that vehicles can see you!\n\nSO HOW FAST ARE WE WALKING?\nT
 he Wednesday Night Walk is about 2.5 mph (22 - 23 minute miles)\nThe Tuesd
 ay Night Fitness Hike nearly 3.5 - 4.0 mph (we target a 16 minute mile\, w
 ith multiple hills!)\n\nHOW DO YOU PARTICIPATE?\nSign up with Meetup and R
 SVP Today! This also gets you on our email list to make you aware of upcom
 ing events\, hikes and walks.\n\nWHY DO YOU NEED TO RSVP?\n\nPlease take t
 he time to RSVP YES when you plan on attending an event. It is equally imp
 ortant to keep your RSVP up to date. If you've RSVP'd YES for an event\, w
 e are going to wait for you until the departure time. We leave promptly at
  6:10 PM\, so if you arrive late you can join us along the route. We typic
 ally hike the same route for each hike\, and our focus is on aerobic exerc
 ise.\n\nQUESTIONS?\nEmail me with any questions by using the "Contact Us" 
 link on the left hand side bar of this meetup group page.\n\nHope to see y
 ou on a walk or hike soon!\n\nSCO Organizers
